solution.p:
The instantaneous percentage rate of change for R is


100\frac{R'}{R}&=100\frac{(PQ)'}{PQ}&\mbox{R=PQ}

&=100\frac{P'Q+PQ'}{PQ}&\mbox{product rule}

&=100\left[\frac{P'}{P}+\frac{Q'}{Q}\right]&\mbox{simplify}

&=100[0.08-0.02]
=6\%

